    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>释放你的逻辑和创造力，在这个烧脑的机器建造冒险中尽情探索！</strong></h2>Axon Hero 不仅仅是个拼图游戏，它还是一个逻辑与想象力碰撞的创意乐园。在这里，你可以通过建造、编程和征服精心设计的关卡，每个关卡都比上一个更让人脑洞大开。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>建造你的工厂杰作！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/26e23cb1f21f3b769c17d22ee80d49bc.poster.avif?t=1709173757\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/26e23cb1f21f3b769c17d22ee80d49bc.webm?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/26e23cb1f21f3b769c17d22ee80d49bc.mp4?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 设计你自己的复杂工厂，里面有传送带、分流器、颜色转换器等等。<br></li><li> 尝试不同的机器布局，找到每个独特谜题的完美解决方案。<br></li><li> 看着你的杰作在你的逻辑代码指引下运转，见证箱子们在你的电路中穿梭！ </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挑选各种各样的机器！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/3f6b0b27f6332c49cc4d36af2487bcbc.poster.avif?t=1709173757\" width=600 height=112 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/3f6b0b27f6332c49cc4d36af2487bcbc.webm?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/3f6b0b27f6332c49cc4d36af2487bcbc.mp4?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 探索各种各样神奇的机器，每个都拥有独特的功能。<br></li><li> 掌握操纵箱子、改变颜色和控制方向的艺术。<br></li><li> 巧妙地组合机器，攻克越来越难的谜题！ </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>编写你的逻辑代码！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/1e5430bee4ac63db129fcdcfc59f5809.poster.avif?t=1709173757\" width=600 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/1e5430bee4ac63db129fcdcfc59f5809.webm?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1743670/extras/1e5430bee4ac63db129fcdcfc59f5809.mp4?t=1709173757\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 释放你内心的程序员，编写你自己的逻辑电路。<br></li><li> 使用 AND、OR 和 NOT 等逻辑门控制你的机器，用独特的方式解决谜题。<br></li><li> 无需编程经验，只需要拖拽连接，就能让你的天才闪耀！ </li></ul><i> 建造，编程，征服 - Axon Hero 等待着你！</i><br><br>多语言支持可能会在以后添加。",
